{"tid":693940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳降暴雨 華強北手推車載過隧道一程$12","createTime":"2018-06-08T01:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T08:23:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":138,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"130dd82c3ca200a8ad741b25cc03c272c9d1bade","tid":693940,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T01:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180608/large/1528417626_6048.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180608%2Flarge%2F1528417626_6048.jpg&h=a25e0cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受熱帶風暴艾雲尼的外圍氣流影響，今早深圳的南山、寶安、光明、龍華、龍崗、福田、羅湖等地都降大雨，不少民眾都要冒雨上班，地鐵站、行人隧道水浸，在華強北有人將用來搬運貨物的手推車，變成積水隧道專車，每程10元人民幣（約12港元），將趕上班的打工仔運載通過積水。<br />\n<br />\n深圳市氣象部門今早發出暴雨黃色預警，有網民在華強北的隧道拍到有人拿手推車載人通過積水的一幕，這些推車人都用手機掃QR Code收錢，不過，有民眾還是覺得貴，寧可澗水而過。<br />\n<br />\n不少民眾上班時拍下窗外暴雨的景象，批評這麼大雨「是黃色預警」，質疑當局「這麼大的雨居然不停課，不下雨的時候停，真不知道天氣預報還有啥用&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n今日內地進行高考，氣象部門亦特別提醒考生，要提早1小時出門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180608/58291652\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F58291652&d=7i8o4Sq34BBSIKgKlxru8sVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a74c5638\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F58291652&h=1286c5c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180608/58291652</a>"},{"pid":"f4db6eb1229ebf8f880ea3d314c4bf6769d4698d","tid":693940,"uid":8410,"like":109,"dislike":3,"score":106,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T01:57:21.000Z","msg":"過條隧道都要俾錢人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed86022481c968139007095ada5843e99684a57","tid":693940,"uid":1482,"like":103,"dislike":4,"score":99,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"大陸公廁都有人收1蚊<img src=